            "textversion": "<h4><strong>That girl over there at the locker.</strong></h4><br><p><strong>Pointing Style:</strong> When describing what one girl in the room is doing, Chloe points in that direction with just one finger.<br><strong>NMMs: </strong> She puckers her mouth slightly to show a small struggle with her locker sticking.</p><div class='col-xs-8'><iframe src='https://cdnapisec.kaltura.com/p/2061901/sp/206190100/embedIframeJs/uiconf_id/35766781/partner_id/2061901?iframeembed=true&playerId=Kaltura&entry_id=0_4jed23dl' allowfullscreen></iframe></div><div class='hidden'><a class='pop record_icon' data-height='400px' href='../../global/video_recorder/video-only.htm'><img src='../../global/images/record.svg' alt='record image' alt='Select to open recording too.' class='skipimg'> Give It a Try</a></div>",
            "custom_marker": "hotspot_interactive.svg",
            "custom_marker_height": "50",
            "custom_marker_width": "50"
          },
          {
            "top": "50",
            "left": "50",
            "title": "",
            "textversion": "<h4><strong>I don't know the three boys standing behind me.</strong></h4><br><p><strong>Pointing Style:</strong> These three boys are behind Chloe, so she uses three fingers and motions over the shoulder closest to them. <br><strong>NMMs: </strong> She leans her body in their direction and uses her face to indicate 'don't' know.</p><div class='col-xs-8'><iframe src='https://cdnapisec.kaltura.com/p/2061901/sp/206190100/embedIframeJs/uiconf_id/35766781/partner_id/2061901?iframeembed=true&playerId=Kaltura&entry_id=0_5mnnk9yw' allowfullscreen></iframe></div><div class='hidden'><a class='pop record_icon' data-height='400px' href='../../global/video_recorder/video-only.htm'><img src='../../global/images/record.svg' alt='record image' alt='Select to open recording too.' class='skipimg'> Give It a Try</a></div>",
            "custom_marker": "hotspot_interactive.svg",
            "custom_marker_height": "50",
            "custom_marker_width": "50"
          },
          {
            "top": "100",
            "left": "100",
            "title": "",
            "textversion": "<h4><strong>Those two girls, they are walking.</strong></h4><br><p><strong>Pointing Style:</strong> Since there are two girls present and walking, Chloe uses two fingers in motion as she points in their direction.</p><div class='col-xs-8'><iframe src='https://cdnapisec.kaltura.com/p/2061901/sp/206190100/embedIframeJs/uiconf_id/35766781/partner_id/2061901?iframeembed=true&playerId=Kaltura&entry_id=0_qe75pxe7' allowfullscreen></iframe></div><div class='hidden'><a class='pop record_icon' data-height='400px' href='../../global/video_recorder/video-only.htm'><img src='../../global/images/record.svg' alt='record image' alt='Select to open recording too.' class='skipimg'> Give It a Try</a></div>",
            "custom_marker": "hotspot_interactive.svg",
            "custom_marker_height": "50",
            "custom_marker_width": "50"
          },
          {
            "top": "150",
            "left": "150",
            "title": "",
            "textversion": "<h4><strong>That boy over there, he has brown hair and a black backpack.</strong></h4><br> <p><strong>Pointing Style:</strong> Chloe's talking about one boy who's in the room, so she uses one finger and points in his direction. <br><strong>NMMs: </strong>She shifts her body in his direction and uses head tilting.</p><div class='col-xs-8'><iframe src='https://cdnapisec.kaltura.com/p/2061901/sp/206190100/embedIframeJs/uiconf_id/35766781/partner_id/2061901?iframeembed=true&playerId=Kaltura&entry_id=0_jaap6esx' allowfullscreen></iframe></div><div class='hidden'><a class='pop record_icon' data-height='400px' href='../../global/video_recorder/video-only.htm'><img src='../../global/images/record.svg' alt='record image' alt='Select to open recording too.' class='skipimg'> Give It a Try</a></div>",
            "custom_marker": "hotspot_interactive.svg",
            "custom_marker_height": "50",
            "custom_marker_width": "50"
          },
          {
            "top": "200",
            "left": "200",
            "title": "",
            "textversion": "<h4><strong>We are going to class together.</strong></h4><br><p><strong>Pointing Style:</strong> See how Chloe is referring to herself and the collective group? For that, she uses a designated handshape to show a group and the direction of its movement.<br><strong>NMMs: </strong> Watch how she uses her body's natural motion to shift forward with her hands.</p><div class='col-xs-8'><iframe src='https://cdnapisec.kaltura.com/p/2061901/sp/206190100/embedIframeJs/uiconf_id/35766781/partner_id/2061901?iframeembed=true&playerId=Kaltura&entry_id=0_ipgh6fij' allowfullscreen></iframe></div><div class='hidden'><a class='pop record_icon' data-height='400px' href='../../global/video_recorder/video-only.htm'><img src='../../global/images/record.svg' alt='record image' alt='Select to open recording too.' class='skipimg'> Give It a Try</a></div>",
